title: Mastercam X9 Build 18.0.11898.0  (X64) + medicine
description:
Mastercam X9 Build 18.0.11898.0 (x64) | 1.44 GB
Mastercam offers CAD / CAM-tools for all types of programming - from simple to very complex. The system has everything you need for your production - milling of two to five axes, turning, turning, milling, wire electroerosion, woodworking, art modeling and complex 3D-engraving. Mastercam Design allows you to import data from all known of CAD-systems, as well as free space to design 3D-shapes using all the necessary for this set of tools, including wireframe and surface modeling, solid modeling, free hybrid modeling, drawing and automatic reception of sketches and drawings. The choice of Mastercam module depends on for what tasks it is supposed to use
